{"word":"πλέως","slug":"πλέως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πλέως</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πίμπλημι'><el>πίμπλημι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>full of</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>πλεῖαι οἴνου κλισίαι</el> <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>ράκη νοσηλείας πλέα</el> rags <i>infected with</i> his sore, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>full</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of Time, <i>full, complete</i>, <el>δέκα πλείους ἐνιαυτούς</el> ten <i>full</i> years, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a> <el>πλειότερος</el> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}